# React Login Authentication App

A simple React-based login and registration system with client-side authentication using `localStorage`.  
Users can register, login, and access a secure page. Includes form validation and error handling.

---

## Features

- User registration with name, email, and password
- User login with email and password
- Client-side form validation (email format, password length, password confirmation)
- Persistent login state using `localStorage`
- Secure page accessible only after login
- Logout functionality
- Responsive and clean UI with Tailwind CSS styling
- Icons from `lucide-react`

